The paper focuses on multiagent teaming, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multiagent systems (cs.MA). The use of POMDPs and optimization techniques falls under robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques to improve performance, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG).
